<h2 id="research" class="govuk-heading-l">Research</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
The pattern is used in the VAT repayments service. Usability testing took place with 7 users as part of 3 rounds of research.  </p>
 <p class="govuk-body"> The rearch showed that users understood that the:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet" role="list">
<li> events were related to each other
  <li> one event followed another event</li>
<li> top event was the most recent </li>
</ul>

